    <p><strong>2. Ethical Refinement — ‘sādhu-bhāve’:</strong> The expression <em>sādhu-bhāva</em> introduces the dimension of goodness and integrity. It reflects actions performed with sincerity, honesty, and alignment. This is not morality imposed externally but an internal coherence where thought, intention, and action are unified. Such alignment eliminates inner conflict and creates a sense of harmony.</p>

