    <p><strong>Conclusion:</strong> This verse expands the meaning of “Sat” beyond a philosophical concept into a practical guide for action. It connects truth, goodness, and right action into a single framework. When actions are aligned with <em>Sat</em>, they gain stability and depth, transcending temporary motivations. This alignment transforms ordinary actions into expressions of truth, gradually refining both the individual and their engagement with the world.</p>
